biotools.summary:
An R package to explore the propagation of extinctions through complex ecological networks.

Extinction Simulation in Food Webs.

The NetworkExtinction package contains the following man pages: chilean_intertidal CompareExtinctions degree_distribution ExtinctionOrder ExtinctionPlot Less_Connected More_Connected Mostconnected net RandomExtinctions.
